(This project is modular by domain. Below is a quick map of every top?level module under Src/ and) Tj
T*
(its role.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Accounts/) Tj
T*
(- Key management \(Falcon keys, export/import, format enforcement\).) Tj
T*
(- Src/Api/) Tj
T*
(- FastAPI app, auth, API routes \(wallet, chain, tx, mining, peers\).) Tj
T*
(- Src/Blockchain/) Tj
T*
(- Core blockchain logic \(block model, chain validation, genesis, reorg/orphan handling\).) Tj
T*
(- Src/Config/) Tj
T*
(- Config files \(API keys, port mappings, bootstrap seeds, etc.\).) Tj
T*
(- Src/Falcon/) Tj
T*
(- Falcon signature integration and CLI/binaries.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Kyber/) Tj
T*
(- Vendored Kyber KEM implementation and wrappers used by wallet lockbox workflows.) Tj
T*
(- Src/GUI/) Tj
T*
(- Desktop GUI, CLI UI, Web Explorer \(web_explorer.html\), and local explorer bridge server.) Tj
T*
