T*
(- Launchers and main entrypoints \(runnode.py, emission bootstrap, etc.\).) Tj
T*
(- Src/Miner/) Tj
T*
(- Mining loop, PoW manager, candidate block building.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Network/) Tj
T*
(- P2P server, peer manager, sync logic, bootstrap/seed handling, network logs.) Tj
T*
(- Src/SigWit/) Tj
T*
(- Witness model, commitments, wtxid logic, pruning helpers.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Storage/) Tj
T*
(- LMDB stores for blocks, UTXO, mempool, and orphan branches.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Transactions/) Tj
T*
(- Transaction model, inputs/outputs, signing, verification, coinbase.) Tj
T*
(- Src/Utility/) Tj
T*
